Given the following class A address: 10.0.0.0/24,
1 - How many bits have been borrowed from the HostID section?

	16



2 - What is this networkâ€™s subnetwork mask? (Decimal and binary representation)
	
	dec : 255.255.255.0
	bin : 1111 1111.1111 1111.1111 1111.0000 0000



3 - How many subnetworks are there? How many hosts per subnetwork?

	65536 (2^16) : 254



4 - What is the network address and the broadcast address of the 16th subnetwork?
	
	net : 10.0.15.0
	broad : 10.0.15.255



5 - What is the network address and the broadcast address of the last subnetwork?

	net : 10.255.255.0
	broad : 10.255.255.255



6 - What is the network address and the broadcast address of the primary network?
	net : 10.0.0.0
	broad : 10.255.255.255
